1
00:00:10,719 --> 00:00:13,888
Jonathan! Nancy! Jonathan!

2
00:00:14,764 --> 00:00:16,349
Jonathan! Nancy!

3
00:00:18,601 --> 00:00:19,436
Apa kau buat?

4
00:00:19,519 --> 00:00:22,689
Dengar sini! Jangan sentuh apa-apa!

5
00:00:36,536 --> 00:00:37,787
Mungkin tak kena?

6
00:00:54,763 --> 00:00:56,723
- Mungkin kita patut…
- Ya.

7
00:01:40,725 --> 00:01:45,396
Sebelum itu, saya tahu sekarang 5.00 pagi,
tapi tolong bina penjejak telemetri.

8
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:47,273
Apa? Erica, sekarang…

9
00:01:47,357 --> 00:01:49,359
5.00 pagi. Dia dah cakap tadi.

10
00:01:49,442 --> 00:01:51,611
Maaf. Awak siapa pula?

11
00:01:51,694 --> 00:01:53,738
- Pak cik saya.
- Penjaga dia.

12
00:01:53,822 --> 00:01:55,115
Siapa itu, manja?

13
00:01:55,198 --> 00:01:59,035
Tak apa, cinta. Tidurlah dulu.
Sekejap lagi saya datang.

14
00:01:59,119 --> 00:02:00,328
Okey.

15
00:02:00,411 --> 00:02:01,663
Pustakawan kita?

16
00:02:01,746 --> 00:02:03,832
Kalau mengerang, dia suruh diam?

17
00:02:03,915 --> 00:02:10,130
Okey, kamu dan sesiapa pun awak,
kamu tak patut datang macam ini.

18
00:02:10,213 --> 00:02:12,173
Kita jumpa di kelas nanti, Erica.

19
00:02:13,341 --> 00:02:15,343
Dustin dalam bahaya.

20
00:02:16,010 --> 00:02:18,138
Bahaya? Bahaya macam mana?

21
00:02:18,221 --> 00:02:19,848
Soal hidup atau mati.

22
00:02:19,931 --> 00:02:21,182
Macam mana, manja?

23
00:02:21,266 --> 00:02:23,059
Awak nak main dengan ulat buku

24
00:02:23,143 --> 00:02:26,062
atau bina penjejak
dan selamatkan pelajar awak?

25
00:02:29,232 --> 00:02:30,066
Henderson!

26
00:02:30,942 --> 00:02:31,776
Dustin!

27
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,528
Dustin. Hei.

28
00:02:33,611 --> 00:02:34,737
Apa benda tadi?

29
00:02:34,821 --> 00:02:36,990
Penjana perisai? Mereka dah jumpa?

30
00:02:37,073 --> 00:02:38,116
Aku silap.

31
00:02:38,825 --> 00:02:40,368
Betul-betul tersilap

32
00:02:41,619 --> 00:02:43,037
sampai membawa bencana.

33
00:02:43,121 --> 00:02:44,205
Apa?

34
00:02:44,289 --> 00:02:46,332
Lepas kau pergi, aku jumpa jurnal.

35
00:02:47,041 --> 00:02:48,626
Jurnal Brenner.

36
00:02:50,170 --> 00:02:53,381
Kunci untuk musnahkan tembok itu
ada di makmal ini,

37
00:02:53,464 --> 00:02:56,050
tapi ia bukan penjana perisai.

38
00:02:56,134 --> 00:02:58,636
Ia bukan sihir gelap. Vecna tak bina.

39
00:03:02,056 --> 00:03:03,391
Sains yang bina.

40
00:03:04,809 --> 00:03:07,979
Ahli fizik teori menggelarnya
sebagai jirim eksotik.

41
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:11,983
Satu sumber tenaga
yang mendirikan tembok gergasi itu.

42
00:03:12,066 --> 00:03:14,569
Aku rasa Nancy baru saja tembak jirim itu.

43
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:28,541
Apa masalahnya?
Kita memang nak lepasi tembok itu.

44
00:03:28,625 --> 00:03:30,627
- Kau tak dengar!
- Aku dengar.

45
00:03:30,710 --> 00:03:33,254
Vecna tak bina.
Dia tak ada di sebelah sana.

46
00:03:33,338 --> 00:03:36,299
Holly dan budak-budak itu pun tak ada.

47
00:03:37,675 --> 00:03:39,636
Habis, apa ada di sebelah sana?

48
00:03:49,812 --> 00:03:51,105
Kenapa ia terhenti?

49
00:03:57,779 --> 00:04:00,031
Dustin, apa ada di sebelah sana?

50
00:04:00,823 --> 00:04:01,658
Maut.

51
00:04:11,834 --> 00:04:14,087
Sudah! Sudah, mari pergi!

52
00:04:15,421 --> 00:04:16,798
Cepat!

53
00:04:17,507 --> 00:04:18,633
Lari!

54
00:04:19,342 --> 00:04:20,468
Tunduk!

55
00:04:30,687 --> 00:04:32,397
Selama ini,

56
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:35,650
segala andaian kita
tentang Tempat Terbalik

57
00:04:36,484 --> 00:04:37,944
betul-betul salah.

58
00:04:42,991 --> 00:04:44,033
Pintu itu!

59
00:04:44,617 --> 00:04:45,743
Pintu itu!

60
00:04:46,869 --> 00:04:48,663
Saya boleh kosongkan laluan!

61
00:04:48,746 --> 00:04:52,834
Jangan! Ikut di belakang! Belakang saya!

62
00:04:52,917 --> 00:04:54,919
Tidak! Tak guna!

63
00:05:04,345 --> 00:05:05,346
Berhenti!

64
00:05:06,014 --> 00:05:07,056
Jangan!

65
00:05:19,777 --> 00:05:22,322
Tempat ini, Tempat Terbalik,

66
00:05:22,405 --> 00:05:24,157
ia bukan dimensi lain.

67
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,992
Ia bukan dunia lain.

68
00:05:26,075 --> 00:05:27,702
Ia sebenarnya lubang ulir.

69
00:05:27,785 --> 00:05:28,786
Sebuah jambatan

70
00:05:29,579 --> 00:05:33,791
antara dua titik dalam masa dan ruang,
antara dunia kita dan dunia lain.

71
00:05:33,875 --> 00:05:35,460
Kalau jambatan itu runtuh?

72
00:05:35,543 --> 00:05:37,378
Ia akan menarik kita sekali.

73
00:05:39,922 --> 00:05:41,049
Kita semua.

74
00:07:03,464 --> 00:07:10,471
BABAK ENAM: MELARIKAN DIRI DARI CAMAZOTZ

75
00:07:41,043 --> 00:07:42,503
Masuk, masuk!

76
00:07:47,467 --> 00:07:49,051
Awak okey tak?

77
00:07:49,552 --> 00:07:50,386
Tak apa.

78
00:07:51,179 --> 00:07:53,306
Kita selamat. Dia tak boleh masuk.

79
00:07:53,389 --> 00:07:54,265
Max…

80
00:08:03,858 --> 00:08:05,109
Holly!

81
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:06,861
Jom.

82
00:08:10,823 --> 00:08:11,866
Holly, sayang.

83
00:08:11,949 --> 00:08:14,076
Berhenti, atau saya akan sakiti dia.

84
00:08:16,204 --> 00:08:20,416
Saya tahu awak anggap Max kawan awak.

85
00:08:21,042 --> 00:08:25,254
Tapi dia dah perdayakan awak, Holly.
Dia dah cemarkan minda awak.

86
00:08:25,338 --> 00:08:27,215
Dia pembohong.

87
00:08:27,298 --> 00:08:29,634
Tak! Tak, kaulah pembohong!

88
00:08:29,717 --> 00:08:32,011
Aku dah nampak diri kau yang sebenar!

89
00:08:32,094 --> 00:08:33,137
Kau raksasa!

90
00:08:33,221 --> 00:08:35,306
Raksasa yang menjijikkan!

91
00:08:35,389 --> 00:08:36,849
Holly!

92
00:08:36,933 --> 00:08:40,520
Kalau awak tak ikut saya balik
kepada budak-budak lain,

93
00:08:40,603 --> 00:08:43,272
saya terpaksa sakiti Max.

94
00:08:47,026 --> 00:08:49,153
Mungkin saya perlu bunuh dia.

95
00:08:49,237 --> 00:08:51,405
Habis, kenapa kau tak bunuh?

96
00:08:52,114 --> 00:08:53,074
Aku ada di sini.

97
00:08:53,157 --> 00:08:54,909
Oh, ya.

98
00:08:54,992 --> 00:08:57,620
Kau takut sangat dengan gua bodoh ini.

99
00:08:57,703 --> 00:08:59,288
Dasar pengecut!

100
00:08:59,956 --> 00:09:02,792
Keadaan dah berubah sekarang, Max.

101
00:09:03,834 --> 00:09:07,255
Ada cara lain untuk aku dapatkan kau.

102
00:09:07,838 --> 00:09:08,839
Holly?

103
00:09:09,966 --> 00:09:13,177
Apabila kawan baharu awak mula menderita,

104
00:09:14,595 --> 00:09:16,180
dia pasti akan menderita,

105
00:09:16,889 --> 00:09:20,309
awak boleh kembali kepada saya
dan tamatkan penderitaan dia

106
00:09:21,018 --> 00:09:23,396
atau tengok kawan baharu awak itu mati.

107
00:09:24,230 --> 00:09:25,982
Nyawa dia di tangan awak.

108
00:09:38,828 --> 00:09:43,499
6 NOVEMBER

109
00:10:10,401 --> 00:10:14,947
Boleh tak sesiapa tolong jelaskan
apa sebenarnya yang berlaku?

110
00:10:15,031 --> 00:10:18,743
Kita dah hanguskan zarahnya.
Aku nampak semuanya terbang.

111
00:10:18,826 --> 00:10:21,245
- Kamu nampak, bukan?
- Mestilah nampak.

112
00:10:21,329 --> 00:10:23,623
Will sepatutnya terputus
daripada minda sarang.

113
00:10:23,706 --> 00:10:25,791
- Itu teori.
- Kenapa dia tak sedar?

114
00:10:25,875 --> 00:10:27,752
Kenapa dia nampak Max pula?

115
00:10:27,835 --> 00:10:30,630
Betulkah? Vecna nak kelirukan kita lagi?

116
00:10:30,713 --> 00:10:32,506
Tak masuk akal langsung!

117
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:37,094
Doktor-doktor pun tak faham
kenapa Max koma, bukan?

118
00:10:37,178 --> 00:10:38,721
Apa? Tak. Kenapa?

119
00:10:40,848 --> 00:10:43,934
Okey. Okey, okey.

120
00:10:44,018 --> 00:10:47,730
Anggaplah semua yang Will nampak
memang betul-betul terjadi.

121
00:10:47,813 --> 00:10:50,066
- Max dengan Holly.
- Ya, macam mana?

122
00:10:50,149 --> 00:10:51,317
Sabar.

123
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:53,194
Katakanlah

124
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:55,321
ini Will,

125
00:10:55,404 --> 00:10:58,824
dan ini Holly.

126
00:10:58,908 --> 00:10:59,784
Kemudian,

127
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:03,621
ini pula, tentulah Max.

128
00:11:04,580 --> 00:11:07,416
Mereka di tiga lokasi berbeza,
Squawk, hospital,

129
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:09,752
dan suatu tempat di Tempat Terbalik.

130
00:11:09,835 --> 00:11:11,045
- Betul.
- Ya.

131
00:11:11,128 --> 00:11:14,757
Tapi mereka ada satu persamaan
yang sangat penting.

132
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,217
Mereka semua tak sedar.

133
00:11:18,719 --> 00:11:20,179
Apa jadi jika ditangkap Vecna?

134
00:11:20,846 --> 00:11:22,056
Kita akan bersawai.

135
00:11:22,139 --> 00:11:24,225
Keadaannya serupa macam koma.

136
00:11:24,308 --> 00:11:27,478
Patutlah doktor bingung.
Max tak koma pun sebenarnya.

137
00:11:27,561 --> 00:11:29,188
Dia bersawai.

138
00:11:29,772 --> 00:11:32,692
Sama macam Will. Sama macam Holly.

139
00:11:33,275 --> 00:11:36,487
Saya rasa semua dah cukup jelas sekarang.

140
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:38,155
Mungkin minda mereka

141
00:11:39,281 --> 00:11:40,700
ada di tempat yang sama?

142
00:11:41,784 --> 00:11:43,077
Dalam minda Vecna.

143
00:11:44,453 --> 00:11:45,538
Terpenjara.

144
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:48,290
Sebelum ini.

145
00:11:48,374 --> 00:11:49,583
Kalau Will betul,

146
00:11:49,667 --> 00:11:53,754
Max dan Holly
tengah cuba lari dari penjara.

147
00:11:53,838 --> 00:11:55,297
Kalau mereka berjaya,

148
00:11:55,381 --> 00:11:58,759
mereka akan kembali kepada tubuh mereka,

149
00:11:59,552 --> 00:12:02,388
dan Max akan hidup semula.

150
00:12:02,471 --> 00:12:05,266
Mereka betul-betul ada dalam minda Vecna.

151
00:12:05,349 --> 00:12:07,309
Mereka tahu semuanya. Tahu Will di mana.

152
00:12:07,393 --> 00:12:09,603
- Budak-budak itu di mana.
- Rancangan Vecna.

153
00:12:09,687 --> 00:12:12,732
- Fasa akhir.
- Nasib planet ini mungkin terletak

154
00:12:12,815 --> 00:12:16,402
di tangan kekasih awak yang koma
dan adik perempuan awak.

155
00:12:16,485 --> 00:12:18,320
Kita boleh cuba lagi, bukan?

156
00:12:18,404 --> 00:12:19,947
- Boleh pandu?
- Cuma tiada lesen.

157
00:12:20,030 --> 00:12:22,116
Tak apa. Bawa kereta Joyce.
Jangan kena tahan.

158
00:12:22,199 --> 00:12:23,701
Teman Max. Saya teman Will.

159
00:12:23,784 --> 00:12:24,785
Okey.

160
00:13:04,116 --> 00:13:06,160
Kau ingat lagi tempat ini,

161
00:13:07,787 --> 00:13:08,662
William?

162
00:13:13,125 --> 00:13:16,837
Semua ini membangkitkan…

163
00:13:21,383 --> 00:13:22,593
memori kau?

164
00:13:23,719 --> 00:13:25,638
Max. Holly.

165
00:13:27,139 --> 00:13:28,808
Mereka dapat lari, bukan?

166
00:13:30,226 --> 00:13:32,228
Kaki kau melambatkan kau?

167
00:13:32,311 --> 00:13:35,397
Kau ingat kau pandai sangat, ya?

168
00:13:35,981 --> 00:13:38,275
Tapi ingat.

169
00:13:38,359 --> 00:13:41,320
Akulah yang berkuasa.

170
00:13:41,904 --> 00:13:44,365
Aku yang bawa kau masuk.

171
00:13:45,491 --> 00:13:48,285
Kau wadah aku.

172
00:13:49,245 --> 00:13:50,746
Pengintip aku.

173
00:13:52,331 --> 00:13:54,083
Pembina aku.

174
00:13:55,376 --> 00:13:56,377
Pembina?

175
00:13:59,755 --> 00:14:03,217
Kau rasa macam mana
semua terowong itu boleh ada, William?

176
00:14:05,845 --> 00:14:08,889
Kau yang bina

177
00:14:08,973 --> 00:14:13,561
setiap kali kau tidur malam.

178
00:14:19,984 --> 00:14:22,820
Ada begitu banyak kuasa dalam diri kau.

179
00:14:23,654 --> 00:14:26,365
Tapi jangan salah faham.

180
00:14:27,449 --> 00:14:30,327
Itu sebenarnya kuasa aku,

181
00:14:30,411 --> 00:14:34,623
dan ia lebih kuat daripada sebelum ini.

182
00:14:38,961 --> 00:14:41,547
Jauh lebih kuat.

183
00:14:51,974 --> 00:14:54,268
Akhirnya, masanya sudah tiba.

184
00:14:55,394 --> 00:15:01,066
Masa untuk wadah-wadah aku
membawa kita ke dunia baharu.

185
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:04,403
Dunia yang lebih baik.

186
00:15:05,321 --> 00:15:09,992
Malangnya, dunia kau takkan wujud

187
00:15:10,075 --> 00:15:13,078
sebab Max dah bawa lari
salah seorang wadah kau.

188
00:15:13,662 --> 00:15:17,791
Ada caranya untuk buat musang keluar
dari sarangnya, William.

189
00:15:17,875 --> 00:15:20,294
Kau akan tolong aku.

190
00:15:20,377 --> 00:15:25,049
Kau akan jadi pengintip aku

191
00:15:25,132 --> 00:15:29,094
buat kali terakhir.

192
00:15:29,178 --> 00:15:30,095
Tidak.

193
00:15:30,679 --> 00:15:31,555
Jangan harap.

194
00:15:42,274 --> 00:15:44,777
Semakin kuat kau melawan,

195
00:15:46,195 --> 00:15:48,739
semakin perit rasanya.

196
00:16:15,766 --> 00:16:16,767
Bodoh.

197
00:16:21,772 --> 00:16:23,107
- Hei!
- Apa awak buat?

198
00:16:23,190 --> 00:16:24,566
Tengok kalau dia ada.

199
00:16:24,650 --> 00:16:25,859
- Tiada.
- Mana tahu?

200
00:16:25,943 --> 00:16:28,696
Sebab dia tahu dia tak boleh masuk. Jom.

201
00:16:28,779 --> 00:16:32,032
Dia kata keadaan dah berubah,
dan dia ada cara lain.

202
00:16:32,116 --> 00:16:35,160
Ya, dia kuat temberang.
Awak sepatutnya dah tahu.

203
00:16:35,244 --> 00:16:39,915
Jadi, apa patut kita buat?
Duduk diam saja? Terima takdir kita?

204
00:16:39,999 --> 00:16:41,375
Tak, kita tak terima.

205
00:16:41,458 --> 00:16:43,711
Terus hidup sampai kita diselamatkan.

206
00:16:43,794 --> 00:16:45,129
Oleh Eleven?

207
00:16:45,879 --> 00:16:47,256
Mana awak tahu itu dia?

208
00:16:47,339 --> 00:16:49,633
Siapa lagi yang ada kuasa psikik,

209
00:16:49,717 --> 00:16:52,177
boleh memasuki minda Vecna dari jauh,

210
00:16:52,261 --> 00:16:56,306
lawan dia, berkomunikasi menerusi dia
dan suruh kita lari selain El?

211
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:59,476
Dia tahu kita di sini.
Dia akan selamatkan kita.

212
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:01,645
Boleh tak berhenti mundar-mandir?

213
00:17:01,729 --> 00:17:04,273
Serius, gaya awak macam abang awak.

214
00:17:08,235 --> 00:17:09,278
Terima kasih.

215
00:17:15,659 --> 00:17:17,953
Kenapa Henry tak boleh masuk ke sini?

216
00:17:18,037 --> 00:17:19,246
Saya pun tak tahu.

217
00:17:20,414 --> 00:17:22,750
Dua tahun awak duduk saja di sini.

218
00:17:24,001 --> 00:17:25,461
Mesti awak ada teori.

219
00:17:28,797 --> 00:17:31,967
Kalau kita nak tunggu saja,
baik kita berbual.

220
00:17:38,682 --> 00:17:40,184
- Penjara ini…
- Camazotz.

221
00:17:40,267 --> 00:17:42,269
Camazotz. Baik.

222
00:17:44,521 --> 00:17:46,940
Ia terdiri daripada memori Henry, betul?

223
00:17:47,816 --> 00:17:50,444
Termasuk gua ini.

224
00:17:50,527 --> 00:17:54,031
Jadi, saya rasa mungkin ini

225
00:17:54,698 --> 00:17:56,909
suatu memori yang entah kenapa,

226
00:17:56,992 --> 00:17:59,119
Henry tak mahu hadapi.

227
00:18:00,370 --> 00:18:01,747
Sesuatu yang traumatik.

228
00:18:03,415 --> 00:18:07,711
Tapi tak ada apa-apa pun di sini
yang menakutkan langsung, jadi,

229
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:09,421
mungkin bukan.

230
00:18:11,924 --> 00:18:13,509
Itulah teori saya.

231
00:18:15,010 --> 00:18:16,011
Saya suka.

232
00:18:18,555 --> 00:18:19,389
Terima kasih.

233
00:18:19,973 --> 00:18:22,851
Kalau betullah cakap awak,

234
00:18:24,436 --> 00:18:27,439
mungkin kita boleh lari
menerusi memori ini.

235
00:18:28,023 --> 00:18:29,358
- Apa?
- Okey, jadi…

236
00:18:30,150 --> 00:18:33,362
Rumah saya, loteng awak,
itu pun memori yang traumatik.

237
00:18:33,445 --> 00:18:35,447
Ia bawa kita keluar dari Camazotz.

238
00:18:35,531 --> 00:18:38,075
Mungkin memori Henry pun
boleh buat begitu.

239
00:18:38,158 --> 00:18:41,036
Macam saya cakap, tak ada apa-apa di sini.

240
