Okey, jadi kita tunggu apa lagi?

294
00:21:47,139 --> 00:21:48,181
Kau nak ke mana?

295
00:21:48,265 --> 00:21:50,934
Cuba dapatkan isyarat untuk cari Nancy.

296
00:21:51,018 --> 00:21:52,769
- Tunggu.
- Jom, Henderson.

297
00:21:52,853 --> 00:21:54,146
- Tunggu.
- Jom!

298
