Abang saya pernah cerita
tentang Pak Cik Eric?

409
00:28:36,631 --> 00:28:37,799
Pak Cik Eric?

410
00:28:37,882 --> 00:28:40,385
Dia pengesan logam. Awak tahu apa itu?

411
00:28:40,468 --> 00:28:41,720
Dia cari logam.

412
