Tolonglah!

434
00:30:21,402 --> 00:30:22,445
Tak guna!

435
00:30:30,245 --> 00:30:31,663
Awak nak buat apa?

436
00:30:31,746 --> 00:30:34,707
Di tingkat bawah,
gayanya askar potong pintu itu.

437
00:30:41,965 --> 00:30:43,258
Jaga-jaga.

438
00:30:47,846 --> 00:30:49,055
Alamak! Ke belakang!

439
00:30:52,308 --> 00:30:53,977
Alamak!

440
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:55,228
Ya Tuhan!

441
00:31:01,943 --> 00:31:02,944
Alamak!

442
00:31:05,572 --> 00:31:08,074
Meja itu! Naik meja itu!

443
